column3: Is being comfortable more important to you than getting ahead?
Are you satisfied to be no better than most other people at your job?
Do you like to make improvements to the way the organization you belong to function?
Do you take initiative to nurture and train people who may be useful in your business
Do you get restless and annoyed when you feel you are wasting time?
Have you always worked hard in order to be the best in your field?
Would you prefer to work with a congenial but incompetent partner rather than a difficult but highly competent one?
Do you tend to plan ahead for your job or career?
Is “getting on in life” important to you?
Are you inclined to read of the success of other rather than do the working of making yourself a success?
Would you describe yourself as being lazy?
Will days often go by without your having done a thing?
Are you inclined to take life as it comes without much planning?
